ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: You'd better work hard to learn well.Yes. It's interesting
It covers both on EE and CS fields

The course basically comprises two parts: mobile computing and wireless networking. The opportunity to work on a final project of our own choice is very interesting and rewarding. But the wireless networking part involves quite a lot of maths.
